Your documents are automatically backed up with thinkParity's secure backup service. If your computer is lost or damaged you can easily recover your data. You need to download and install thinkParity on a new computer, then follow the steps below.

To restore your documents:
1 - Start thinkParity. In the wizard that appears, select the option 'I already have a thinkParity account' and press 'Next'.
2 - Enter your username and password and press 'Next'.
3 - Press 'Login'. Your data including packages and contacts will be restored from the secure thinkParity server.